"I'm Cliffjumper" he said, quickly shaking Sublime's hand, but not
waisting his time. He still wanted to be moody. Firedrill however wanted
to make chat, he didnt enjoy this grim environment. "I'm Firedrill" he
said, holding out his hand, hoping this was a friendly Maximal.
